<b>Good song, make sure your party knows - </b>11/23/01 5:04:33 PM<br>~ <b>Gileas Dreamsinger</b><blockquote>I find this song incredibly useful in mob agro areas, and while exploring.  I have 'rescued' people who are stuck in agro areas and asking for help, by invis, run over, group and walk them to a safe area they know.  This happens a lot for some reason, esp in Lake if Ill, when people get ungrouped...   This is a good way to make a friend, and also part of what I do as a bard, for free, of course, like corpse retrievals.<br>Only time it didnt work was when I was in Lake of Ill, and the guy following me fell behind and went vis.  So, explain to everyone that they need to close the gaps (I do this with manasong as well) so that they know whats up.  I lot of people dont ever play bards, and dont really know what bards do/can do, so I like to make it real clear what is happening, and get group consenus that this *IS* what we are doing.  I do tell them if they dont like it, I dont have to be in the group, and also do warn them that I will selos and run with my drum if things go wrong, and have a RUN FOLLOW ME hotkey setup that comes with this explanation.  Works great.<br>Gileas Dreamsinger</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
